\pard\sa160\sl259\slmult0\qc 1.12: SIGNIFICANCE OF THE STUDY\par

\pard\sa160\sl259\slmult0\b0 The study may aim to identify ways in which the implementation of an online salon system can improve business operations, enhance customer experiences, and increase overall efficiency. This could be particularly significant for the growth and success of the salon and spa enterprises.\par
Entrepreneurs, business owners, and managers in the salon and spa industry stand to benefit from the study's revelations about the strategic decisions that contribute to success in the digital landscape. This includes insights into technology adoption, operational adjustments, and customer engagement strategies that are aligned with the entrepreneurial background.\par
With the beauty and wellness industry undergoing a transformation through digitalization, the study addresses the challenges and opportunities associated with integrating online salon systems. Uncovering the nuances of technological adoption can guide businesses in overcoming hurdles and harnessing the full potential of these systems.\par
By exploring the impact of entrepreneurs' experience on the online salon system, the study aims to shed light on how these systems influence customer experiences. Understanding customer preferences and behaviors in the digital realm is essential for delivering services that align with evolving expectations, thus fostering customer satisfaction and loyalty.\par
